1️⃣ RateLimiter (Resilience4j)

Suppose your API suddenly receives too many requests.
Normal traffic → 50 req/sec
Sudden spike → 5000 req/sec

Your service can crash due to:

CPU overload
Thread pool exhaustion
Database overload

