------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bulkhead

Purpose:

Protect threads from exhaustion

Example:

Too many concurrent requests → reject extra requests

Exception:

BulkheadFullException

------------------------------------------------------------------------
2️⃣ RateLimiter

Purpose:

Limit number of requests per time window

Example:

5 requests allowed in 10 seconds

Exception:

RequestNotPermitted
------------------------------------------------------------------------
3️⃣ Retry

Purpose:

Retry temporary failures

Example:

Attempt1 → fail
Attempt2 → success
------------------------------------------------------------------------
4️⃣ TimeLimiter

Purpose:

Stop waiting for slow services

Example:

Timeout = 3 seconds

Exception:

TimeoutException
------------------------------------------------------------------------
5️⃣ CircuitBreaker

Purpose:

Stop repeated failing calls

States:

CLOSED → OPEN → HALF_OPEN

Exception:

CallNotPermittedException
------------------------------------------------------------------------
📌 Failure Protection Summary
Pattern	Protects Against
Bulkhead	                    thread exhaustion
RateLimiter	                    traffic spikes
Retry	                        temporary failure
TimeLimiter	                    slow service
CircuitBreaker	                repeated failures
