What Distributed Tracing Does

Distributed tracing assigns a Trace ID to every request.

Example:

Trace ID = 6f23a9d7

Every service processing that request logs the same trace ID.

What is Zipkin

Zipkin is a distributed tracing system.

It collects tracing data from all services and shows them in a UI.

Zipkins UI shows
Service call timeline
Request latency
Error points
Service dependencies
