OBSERVABILITY:

Observability means the ability to understand what is happening inside a system using external outputs.

In microservices we want to answer:

What happened?
Where did it happen?
Why did it happen?

Observability is built on three core pillars.

Pillar	    Purpose
Logs	    record system events
Metrics	    numerical measurements
Tracing	    request journey across services